Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你刚刚的惨叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蚊子好讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校服还没做好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快来了吧  貌似
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不负责
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟这是定做  要花不少时间的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹你那么娇小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我就是小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈  奈绪  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这个  是母亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近蚊子很猖獗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  帮了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你也是一早起就忙着社团活动？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  游泳池离开放也不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做的事情也不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你这阵子忙完后一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和小悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再没多久游泳池就要开张啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  难道你是旱鸭子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没别的事的话  我要走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要说的其实是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是最棒的取景点对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你就不想再凑近些看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷窥奈绪什么的  这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又没说一定是奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干  干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个男人的话  倒是谁都会想一睹奈绪的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亮平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有搞头哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠那个家伙对你有意思耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成  你去跟小悠说过了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没傻到这地步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是身为男同胞才能懂的一种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你们干脆交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来以为再也见不到的白马王子又出现了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了不要紧了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么还说这种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈绪  到底有什么不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  他肯定是讨厌我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  真是抱歉  小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你这阵子忙完后一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是刻意的  为了不让我伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就好好解释一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么公司手机里会有女人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说了  她是我的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吵了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想摸摸看对吧  小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你慌个什么劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…没什么  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点接通起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…你说网络是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这以前是主要学习家务的女子高中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照传统  女生校服都是要自己缝纽扣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮了我大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有穹  对这活儿都是一窍不通
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再坐一会儿不是挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就现在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少喝杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对茶杯好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直会放到这里  所以小悠家的总是很甜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷在帮人做检查时总会收到些礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就任我泡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好怀念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是这样最好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样和奈绪在一起  最让我舒心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也露个脸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打  打扰了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈绪帮你把纽扣给缝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穹？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  多半是刚睡醒心情不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很合身哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要听客套话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦哦  这萌度超出我的想像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  祝贺你迎来上学第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个中里亮平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穹  请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇  我真想把她愁眉不展的表情给熨平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这很难办哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而萌发我的斗志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很灵验
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  瑛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉球占卜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起肉球占卜的起源
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要追溯到这间叉依姬神社初代神主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照顾一只受伤了的迷途猫的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家好不容易想出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有什么好占卜的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  第二指球  手根球  第四指球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由此得出的占卜结果是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是向心仪已久的对象表白心意的机会！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗  悠你好厉害  走桃花运了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧向奈绪告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠那家伙  真冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白你们想撮合他们两人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为这次一定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明抽到了上上签
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人看不下去  这样的话就要来硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是星期天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  给你做个游泳特训
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午一点集合！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  亮平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:14:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:14:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈绪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈绪是被天女目叫出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.71,0:15:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说请我吃中奖的冰棒  让我教她蝶泳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们彻底中了他们的招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以教教我吗  游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以在游泳池边奔跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍水再用力一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸直手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈绪！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈绪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是从那里进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开门了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实只要我从游泳池那边的门出去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者小悠一个人藏在这里也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为那天的事而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候  父母关系不好  家里一直充满争吵声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天都过得很痛苦  把心里的苦闷都发泄到小悠身上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是随便找个人都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不介意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然第一次的时候十分困惑  说不出话来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于能从这里重新开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今天此刻开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:18.99,pos2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}（奈绪好烦奈绪好烦…）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:21.99,incn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}待续
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------M---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:57.00,title3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(280,120)}咬我耳边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直没收到短信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:22:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也因为害怕不敢发短信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又想起过去被无情甩掉的心理阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.62,0:22:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  初佳姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在路上睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠  永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.55,0:22:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一股很香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.24,0:22:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧了  初佳小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.57,0:22:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还听到很动听的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.61,0:22:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  初佳小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.13,0:23:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你还是换件衣服比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.09,0:23:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  为什么悠会在我的眼前出现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.94,0:23:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.92,0:23:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初佳小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.03,0:23:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘着酒势就…我真是太坏了
